OL,3,CFormer Daily Mail editor calls
OL,4,CBaroness Lawrence's allegations
OL,5,C'bewildering'
OL,7,FFormer Daily Mail editor Paul Dacre
OL,8,Fhas described allegations made by
OL,9,FBaroness Doreen Lawrence against the
OL,10,Fpaper's publisher as "bewildering and
OL,11,Fbitterly wounding", the High Court was
OL,12,Ftold.
OL,14,FThe Duke of Sussex, Sir Elton John,
OL,15,Fand Lady Lawrence are part of a group
OL,16,Fof seven high-profile individuals
OL,17,Fbringing legal action against
OL,18,FAssociated Newspapers Limited (ANL)
OL,19,Fover unlawful information gathering
OL,20,Fallegations.
