OL,3,CFormer Daily Mail editor calls
OL,4,CBaroness Lawrence's allegations
OL,5,C'bewildering'
OL,7,FANL has strongly denied wrongdoing and
OL,8,Fis defending the claims, which are
OL,9,Falso brought by David Furnish, Sir
OL,10,FSimon Hughes, Liz Hurley and Sadie
OL,11,FFrost.
OL,13,FMr Dacre, now editor-in-chief of ANL's
OL,14,Fholding company DMG Media, entered the
OL,15,Fwitness box on Tuesday afternoon as
OL,16,Fthe first witness giving evidence in
OL,17,Fsupport of ANL's defence.
