OL,3,CFormer Daily Mail editor calls
OL,4,CBaroness Lawrence's allegations
OL,5,C'bewildering'
OL,7,FDuring Mr Dacre's tenure as editor,
OL,8,Fthe Daily Mail campaigned to bring the
OL,9,Fkillers of Lady Lawrence's son Stephen
OL,10,Fto justice after his death in 1993.
OL,12,FOn the front page of the paper's
OL,13,FFebruary 14 1997 edition, the paper
OL,14,Flabelled five men ` Gary Dobson, Neil
OL,15,FAcourt, Jamie Acourt, Luke Knight, and
OL,16,FDavid Norris ` as "murderers" and
OL,17,Fchallenged them to sue the newspaper
OL,18,Ffor libel.
