OL,3,CFormer Daily Mail editor calls
OL,4,CBaroness Lawrence's allegations
OL,5,C'bewildering'
OL,7,FIn her claim, Lady Lawrence alleges
OL,8,FANL had targeted her with hidden
OL,9,Felectronic surveillance, as well as
OL,10,Ftapping her landline, monitoring her
OL,11,Fbank account and making payments to
OL,12,Fpolice officers for confidential
OL,13,Finformation, with the court told she
OL,14,Ffelt "like a victim all over again".
OL,16,FAt the start of his evidence, Mr Dacre
OL,17,Ftold the court: "My heart bleeds for
OL,18,FBaroness Doreen Lawrence."
