OL,7,F"Throughout my 26-year editorship,
OL,8,Fthis, of all my countless campaigns,
OL,9,Fmany of which made a significant
OL,10,Fcontribution to the public weal, is
OL,11,Fthe campaign of which I am most proud
OL,12,Fand to which I devoted the most space."
