OL,7,FHe also said it "simply defies reason"
OL,8,Ffor the Daily Mail to use illegal
OL,9,Fmethods to see if other newspapers
OL,10,Fwere getting involved in the Lawrence
OL,11,Fcampaign, later adding: "The
OL,12,Fsuggestion that we ran the campaign to
OL,13,Fgenerate exclusive headlines, sell
OL,14,Fnewspapers and profit is sickeningly
OL,15,Fmisplaced and bleakly cynical."
