OL,4,CBaroness Lawrence's allegations
OL,5,C'bewildering'
OL,7,FCross-examining Mr Dacre, David
OL,8,FSherborne, for the group of household
OL,9,Fnames, asked whether his involvement
OL,10,Fin the case "is motivated by a desire
OL,11,Fto protect your legacy" rather than
OL,12,Fgetting a fair outcome.
OL,14,FMr Dacre replied that while he did
OL,15,Fwish to clear his name, he also cared
OL,16,Fabout the paper and "the honest and
OL,17,Fdedicated staff who work for it".
