OL,7,FBut Mr Sherborne previously told the
OL,8,FLondon court that the Daily Mail and
OL,9,FMail on Sunday had been engaged in
OL,10,Funlawful information gathering over
OL,11,F"at least two decades", and "knew they
OL,12,Fhad skeletons in their closet".
OL,14,FHe said: "There is evidence,
OL,15,Findisputable evidence, in the
OL,16,Fdocuments that Associated journalists
OL,17,Fand senior executives were
OL,18,Fcommissioning and approving the
OL,19,Facquisition and use of unlawfully
OL,20,Fobtained information, and they must
OL,21,Fhave known that.
