OL,5,C'bewildering'
OL,7,F"That is why we say this was no clean
OL,8,Fship, far from it."
OL,10,FMr Sherborne later said that "smoke
OL,11,Fand mirrors" and "carefully
OL,12,Forchestrated attacks" on the claimants
OL,13,Fcould not "save Associated this time".
OL,15,FHe continued: "They have to live by
OL,16,Ftheir all-or-nothing defence."
OL,18,FThe trial before Mr Justice Nicklin is
OL,19,Fdue to conclude in March, with a
OL,20,Fjudgment in writing due at a later
OL,21,Fdate.
